Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,南宋 武當觀\N1262年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李金寶\NLi Jinbao.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒙古人\NMongols.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經摧毀了北峰的道觀\NThey have already destroyed the temple at North Peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-道姑在哪裏  -在東邊道觀裏\N- Where are the nuns? - In the cloisters. East.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.38,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住我們的誓言  我們會血戰到底\NRemember the oath. We fight to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.03,0:00:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得道之人  生死一線\NLife and death are one thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會守護那些書卷\NI will guard the scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李金寶\NLi Jinbao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別殺他\NDo not kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大汗要見他\NThe Khan will want this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬克波羅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百眼特輯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼樣的道士這麼厲害\NWhat kind of monk is able to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.35,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能一人斬殺25名蒙古士兵呢\Nby himself, 25 Mongol soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們道觀裏的巫術嗎\NIs it a form of dark magic practiced at your temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你永遠無從得知\NYou shall never know, shall you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛說什麼\NWhat did you just say, monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛摧毀了一座道觀\NYou destroyed a temple
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那座道觀內珍藏著無數古代卷軸\Nand all of the ancient scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卷軸內就有你想知道的問題的答案\Nthat contained the answers you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在庇護南宋人  而他們是我的敵人\NYou monks were offering shelter to my enemies in South China.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼地方都不能蔑視可汗的命令\NNo place defies the Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你一次\NI will ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還是不說  那你的舌頭就不必留下了\NIf you hold your tongue, I will take your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們藏匿在深山道觀中的武藝到底是什麼\NWhat is this fighting art kept secret in a mountain temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平之術\NThe art of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你折斷了精銳士兵的脖子\NYou break the necks of trained soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,割開他們的喉嚨  將他們像野豬一樣開膛破肚\Ncut their throats, gut them like wild pigs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這是和平\Nand you call it peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毀了一座道觀  還稱其為命運使然呢\NYou destroy a temple and call it destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是先王  絕不會饒恕你\NKings of the past would not have shown you grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.33,0:04:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我  當我攻打一座城池時\NMe, when I make war on a city,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的手藝人我不會趕盡殺絕\NI allow the craftsmen to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我徵召他們  如此他們就得以活命\NI conscript them into service... and they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看這裏\NHere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.72,0:04:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把這種神秘的中原武藝告訴我的軍政大臣\NYou will reveal these Chinese secrets to my war ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教你們中原武藝  好讓你們用來攻擊中原人嗎\NReveal Chinese secrets... to fight the Chinese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證明你自己有用  你才能活下來\NProve yourself useful, you can live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不服從我的命令\NDefy my laws...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的死法會比那些和卷軸一起死去的道士們\Nyou'll die a death far worse than that suffered by the monks
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可怕得多\Nwho perished with your scrolls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我的命令很可笑是嗎\NOh, you find humor in my decree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上只有一個頂級劊子手\NThere is only one Supreme Executioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他那些妄圖取代他的人\NAnd those who try to take his place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好比班門弄斧\Nare like children trying to carve wood as a master carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多只會傷了自己的手\NMost will injure their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不怕死嗎\NYou do not fear death?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不汲汲於活命\NI do not cling to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩者是有區別的\NThere is a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶他下去\NRemove him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這名摔跤手名為黑原野豬\NThis wrestler is named Black Steppe Boar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們在賽西亞俘虜的一名囚犯\NA prisoner captured in Scythia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他為什麼會叫野豬嗎\NDo you know why he is named after the boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他的長相很奇特\NHis resemblance is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被稱作野豬\NHe is called Boar
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為他多次赤手空拳屠殺他人\Nbecause he has killed such without a weapon many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野豬會衝上來  抓住你\NBoar will advance. He will seize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就會展示出你是如何脫出他的掌控的\NYou will demonstrate how to break the grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要蒙上我的眼睛嗎\NYou cover my eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這公平嗎\NIs that just?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大汗想知道你蒙眼之下是如何作戰的\NThe Great Khan wants a report on how you fight blindfolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他真是任性妄為 愚蠢之極\NHe is a most capricious fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是夠膽子的話  就把我的原話傳達給他\NAnd if you were not cowards, you would tell him the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  道士\NQuiet, monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才殺死的將軍是速不台的兒子\NThe general you killed was the son of Subutai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽過這個名字嗎  道士\NDo you know that name, monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\NI do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是成吉思汗手下第一悍將\NGreatest military commander ever to serve Genghis Khan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.75,0:09:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你殺死了他的兒子\NYou slayed his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.89,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是重罪\NThis is a crime beyond crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是\NYet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不汲汲於活命\Nyou do not cling to life, as you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡並無意義\NDeath means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可汗該怎麼辦呢\NWhat is a Khan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經有個商人送了我一隻小亞亞美尼亞的白鶴\NA merchant once gifted me a white crane from Lesser Armenia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是一種十分稀罕的水鳥\Na water bird that was most uncommon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為它一生下來就全身漆黑\Nbecause it had been born all black.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一隻黑色的白鶴\NBlack white crane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這是一種吉兆\NI knew it was an auspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它能給我帶來好運  但是\Nbeing that would bring me fortune, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只黑色的白鶴不願待在我的湖泊裏\Nthat black white crane refused to stay on my lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它總是妄圖飛走\NAlways, it would fly away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的本性在召喚它\NJust its natural calling, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓它給我帶來好運\NI served him and my fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我斷了它一隻翅膀\Nby cutting one wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾王之王\N"By law of the Grand Khan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大汗有旨\NLord of Lords..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我為什麼讓你蒙眼戰鬥\NWhy do you think I had you fight blindfolded?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我任性妄為 愚蠢之極嗎\NBecause I'm a capricious fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是想看看你在黑暗中\NOr to see if you are capable
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能使出你那些道教秘術呢\Nof your Taoist secrets and skills while in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欽此\N"So be it."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到你就知道\NBecause I knew the moment you were presented,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是那種順從的畫家\Nyou would not be like the obedient painter...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.27,0:10:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽天由命的占星家  有酒萬事足的詩人\Nthe resigned astrologer, the noble poet contented with wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會原意順從蒙古帝國\NYou would refuse to serve the Mongol Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到今日\NTo this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只黑色的白鶴還在我的湖上\Nthat black white crane remains on my lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.19,0:11:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我的\NHe is mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之物\Nand he is beloved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在準備好...\NAre you now ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教授我的軍政大臣了嗎\Nto teach my Ministers of Warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給道士上茶\NTea for the monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是和尚  不要給我茶\NDo not confuse me with one of your holy Buddhists.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我酒\NWine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前是因殺害速不台的兒子受罰\NYou were punished for killing the son of Subutai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記這點\NNever forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘的\NI shall not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武當派的道士們窮盡一生\NThe monks of Wudang spend their lives
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.46,0:17:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想達到真正的空性\Ntrying to achieve true emptiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖人只有克服自我\NFor only when the sage can overcome the self
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才能領悟道的真意\Ndoes he enter into the Tao.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是眾謎之外的黑暗之謎\NThat is a dark mystery beyond all mysteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你贈給我的禮物\Nand a gift you gave to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖瞎\NBlind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻能以百眼看世界\NI now see the world with one hundred eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.02,0:17:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給他倒酒\NGive him more wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛抓住了你的馬\NI've just captured your horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.51,0:18:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你\NThen know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武當山上\NThere are four Taoist temples
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有四座道觀\Nstill standing in the Wudang Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人半月後會到那裏把它們都燒成灰\NMy men will go there in a fortnight and burn them to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需我一聲令下\NAt my single command,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信仰的宗教就會從世界上消失\Nyour religion can be wiped off the face of this earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者  它可以繼續存在下去\NOr it can live...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發展\Ngrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,壯大\Nthrive...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.21,0:18:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前提是你向我證明它的價值\Nif you prove its value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.29,0:18:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過訓練你的大臣嗎\NBy training your ministers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個人\NAnd someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定就是王子了吧\NYou must be the prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿爾泰\NI am called Altai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.32,0:19:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你來這裏做什麼\NWhy are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上課\NLessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想通過這些...課程\NAnd what do you intend to teach me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我學到什麼\Nin these... lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你知道  即使是大汗的兒子\NI'm here to teach you that even the son of a royal khan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也知謙恭  知學習\Nis capable of humility and learning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拿起掃帚掃地  阿爾泰\NThen take the broom, Altai, and sweep my floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答得好  如果你相信的話\NGood answer. If only you believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是世界大花園裏的一株小草\NYou are a little nomad weed in the garden of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想讓你長成參天大樹\NThey wish you to grow into a flowering tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棵樹上最重要的部分是什麼\NWhat is the most important part of such a tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樹枝  還有樹上的花\NThe many branches and the flowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我指的是遺產\NI speak of legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你跟我解釋你晦澀的比喻\NThank you for untangling your elusive metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們從根基開始練起\NWe begin with roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能問一個問題嗎\NMay I ask a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.39,0:21:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說\NDo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想在牆上寫字\NIf you wish calligraphy on your wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不找個眼不瞎的書法家來\Nwhy not summon a painter who can see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到我寫的是什麼嗎\NCan you not read the character I made?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它代表的是火\NIt is a symbol for fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.71,0:21:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何異常\NThen what is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.50,0:21:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-倒置了  -沒錯\N- It's upside down. - Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這在功夫世界中代表的是耐心  自控\NThis is the kung fu character for patience, control.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要永遠記住\NRemember this in the future, always,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:21:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不讓憤怒打敗你\N"Never give way to anger."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.91,0:21:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,師父\NSifu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒教過你要保持安靜嗎\NHave I not trained you into exhausted silence yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的課上完了  王子殿下\NToday's lesson is done, My Radiant Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你看不到  但是...\NYou cannot see it, I know. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證  這是由一位\NI assure you it has been overseen
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偉大的漢族建築師\Nby a great Chinese architect...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:23:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用最珍貴的木材和皮草建起來的...\Nmade from the most precious of woods and hides, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大膽\Nimbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人把漢字"火"倒寫在這裏了\NSomeone has painted the character of fire upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我寫的\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,值此新春佳節之際\NOn this day of the New Year...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.86,0:23:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將此處命名為四寶之廳\NI ordain this place the Hall of the Fourth Treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你賜名百眼\NI name you Hundred Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍事大臣\N...Minister of Martial Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以\NAnd so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請你這位武當道士\NI ask of you, as a Wudang priest,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我兒子取一個漢族名字\Ngive my son his Chinese name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從古至今\NThere have been 500 over time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.40,0:23:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已有500多位皇帝統治過中國\Nwho have held the name Emperor of All China,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:23:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們自稱為天子\NSon of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖憑血緣繼承王位\NOrdained by blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其實與統治世界上\Nthere are those who would have been
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最偉大的帝國相比\Nbetter suited to harvest cow dung
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.79,0:24:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人可能更適合去撿牛糞\Nthan to rule the greatest empire on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人就如銀子\NThere are those who were as silver,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.36,0:24:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖不是堅硬無比  但值得鑄幣\Na lesser metal, but worthy of coinage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.15,0:24:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有人...\NAnd then there are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如冰冷的石頭\Nlike cold stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.34,0:24:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全靠蠻力和憤怒\Nwho force their strength and fury
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.27,0:24:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通過威嚇他人贏得皇位\Nand win the title by fear and intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血緣無關緊要\NBlood is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想成為聖賢  靠的是心靈和精神\NHeart and spirit make the sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.98,0:24:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此\NAnd by this...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.45,0:24:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給他取名為真金\NI give this boy the name Jingim.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.87,0:24:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"真正的金子"\N"True gold."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.30,0:25:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣吧\NSo be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.04,0:25:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以後就用這個名字了\NHe will walk out of here with this name,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.90,0:25:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個名字將伴隨他到達聖賢可見的明天\Nand carry it as his own into a tomorrow only the oracles can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.43,0:25:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於你  道士\NAs for you, priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這座道觀歸你了\Nthis temple is yours.
